    "There are widespread reports that students use it for their own work too and there is much handwringing about the potential for cheating.",
    "Indeed, ghostwriters are hard-pressed to compete.",
    "Hence, teachers are keen to know student perceptions and the use of LLM technology like ChatGPT.",
    "LLMs challenge traditional activity by promising to automate important spheres of activity, namely those that operate through rote and repetition.",
    "Assuming that all students use ChatGPT in their work, teachers are forced to change up their lessons to ensure that the students do the learning."
